对特定企业，每一期节目均保有从购车到测试完成的完整视频录像，并有权威机构提供技术支持，相关材料可以提交公证。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b2c4f2047a5938da08e44958c697c83c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "277 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/475036515"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IycWNkJjEtuZEEAMaCDY3ODQzOTcxIKSk+YcGMAw4ugJADnIJNDc1MDM2NTE1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1627437288.0542552", "card_id": "Q_469908655", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《海贼王》世界里，一个人吃两个恶魔果实就会死，为什么海军不喂四皇恶魔果实来变相毒杀他们？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "228 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469908655"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IycWNkJjEtuZEEAMaCDY2NzAzOTE5IM2RhIcGMAU4akAPcgk0Njk5MDg2NTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1627437288.0545692", "card_id": "Q_473665579", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大城市里打拼的年轻人真的像《我在他乡挺好的》里演得一样难吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-af3776ef096ff0fb12a6a24ab18a2572_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "217 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/473665579"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IycWNkJjEtuZEEAMaCDY3NTM4ODg4ILie3ocGMAc43wJAEHIJNDczNjY1NTc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1627437288.0550585", "card_id": "Q_469107554", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 131}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "射击运动员和特种兵谁的枪法更准？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-7f5382c2d57b501854e9b82ed8cd4dc0